		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Charleston&#44; S. C.</placeName> <date>May 2. 1853</date>.</p>
			<p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>&#44; <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">My dear Sir&#33; About 3 weeks ago I addressed<lb/> a letter to you&#44; and must now suppose&#44; that it has been<lb/> miscarried&#44; as I have not yet received any answer of <add>&#63;</add>&#44;<lb/> nor the Occident&#44; for which I have requested you in that letter.<lb/> I therefore would herewith repeat the contents of that letter&#44;<lb/> as far as my recollection serves me.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Being desirous of receiving the Occident regularly&#44;<lb/> you will send the same&#44; commencing with the <date>April</date> No every<lb/> month to my direction&#44; and forward me your bill&#44; through<lb/> your agent in this city&#44;m at your earliest convenience.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">A friend of mine having presented me with a<lb/> full set of the Occident&#44; You would oblige me very much<lb/> by sending me No 1. of Vol. VI. the only missing<lb/> number.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">At the same time I would announce to you&#44; that<lb/> I have&#44; on <date>Pureem</date>&#44; been engaged to <persName>Miss Rachel Ottolengin</persName>&#44;<lb/> daughter of the late <persName>Mr. Ottolengin&#44; Esq.</persName>&#8212;</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Things are going on&#44; in both our congr.&#44; very quietly&#44; and<lb/> thank God&#8212;<sic>peacably</sic>&#59; my colleague&#44; <persName>Rev. Jacobs</persName> preaches<lb/> orthodoxy&#44; my humble self reform&#44; <del>both</del> but we live else on<lb/> the most friendly terms.&#8212;The former however is now a<lb/> little vexed about <persName>Mr Lyons</persName>&#44; who has charged him<lb/> &#36;15.50 for the publication of his letter against you&#44; and</p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p>would not publish his rejoinder to your reply&#8212;covering 28 foolscap&#8212;<lb/>pages&#8212;unless paid for with &#36;50.00. The independent<lb/> paper&#33;&#33;&#33;</p>
          <p rend="indent(5)">Please accept my best regards</p>
          <p rend="indent(6)">Yours most respectfully</p>
          <p rend="indent(7)"><persName role="author">Dr M Mayer</persName></p>
		<pb n="3"/>
			<p><addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>&#44;</p>
